            Course / HTML Fundamentals / <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">Semantic HTML</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Title -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4">
            Semantic HTML – Writing Meaningful Markup
        </h1>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">
            <span>By Jane Smith</span>
            <span>•</span>
